		<div class="question-answer">
			<h2 class="question" id="question">The setter from our team hasn't set the ball properly and it is going a bit further from the middle hitter. You noticed no one besides you can get it. What should you do? </h2>
			
			<h2 class="explanation" id="explanation">You can’t hit the ball over the nets height as your starting positioning is behind the three meters line , also the ball is next to the net, so passing it with the fore arm would make the ball go straight up or to the net , in consequence the best option is to pass it using your finger tips </h2>
		</div>
		
		<div class="answers">
			<div class="answer1" id="answer1">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer1-text">Jump as high as possible and try to hit the ball making sure it goes to the other side</h3>
			</div>
			
			<div class="answer2" id="answer2">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer2-text">Pass it to the other side using your forearms </h3>
			</div>
			
			
			<div class="answer3" id="answer3">
				
				
				<h3 class = "answer3-text">Shout to any of your teammates to let them  know you can’t pass it as your starting position is at the backcour</h3>
			</div>
			
			<div class="answer4" id="answer4">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer4-text">Pass it to the other side using your finger tips</h3>	
			</div>
		</div>
		
